            "title": "Shipping and returns",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<h4><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>Return Policy</strong></span></h4><p><strong>We have a 30-day return policy</strong>, which means you have 30 days after receiving your item to request a return. <br/><br/>To start a return, you can contact us at <a href=\"mailto:contact@griffinfinejewellery.com\">contact@griffinfinejewellery.com</a>. Please note that returns will need to be sent to the following address: 64 South Street, Chichester, PO19 1EE<br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><a href=\"/policies/refund-policy\"><strong>Read our Full Return and Refund Policy Here</strong></a></p><h4><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Click and Collect </span></h4><p>Collect your online orders in our showroom in Chichester, <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">64 South Street, PO19 1EE</span>.</p><p>All orders can be collected in-store.</p><p>You will be notified when your order is ready to collect via e-mail, <strong>this process usually takes 5+ days</strong>, however if any delays become present, you will be notified as soon as possible.</p><p><strong>Please ensure you bring your order confirmation with you when you come to collect your order.</strong></p><h4>Shipping Rates</h4><p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>All Orders over £100 are eligible for Free Royal Mail Special Delivery (UK only)</strong></span></p><p> </p><h5><br/><strong>UK Royal Mail Special Delivery</strong><br/><br/></h5><p><strong>Handling Time: </strong>5+ Business Days</p><p><strong>Delivery Time: </strong>Next Business Day</p><p><strong>Cost:</strong> £12.99</p><p>For more information please visit <a href=\"https://www.royalmail.com/sending/uk/special-delivery-guaranteed-1pm\">RoyalMail.com/UK-Special-Delivery</a></p><h5>International Tracked & Signed (Including EU)</h5><p><strong>Handling Time: </strong>5+ Business Days</p><p><strong>Delivery Time: </strong>3 - 4 Business Days</p><p><strong>Cost:</strong> £15.99</p><p><a href=\"/policies/shipping-policy\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>Read our Full Shipping Policy Here</strong></span></a></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_CdhYDF": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Finance options",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>We've partnered with ClearPay to help you spread the cost of your purchase. At checkout please select ClearPay as a payment method.</p>",
