      "type": "image-with-text",
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "layout": "right",
        "title": "Keep Your Memories In Your Bespoke Engagement Ring",
        "text": "<p>Add some extra sparkle and sentiment by upcycling your heirlooms. If Mum has handed down her old ring, or Grandma wants you to repurpose her ruby pendant, you can keep your precious family memories close by including your heirloom gemstones in the ring you propose with! Find out more about our heirloom remodelling package here.</p><p>If you’d like to change a little more than the shape of one of our existing designs, we also offer bespoke wedding rings! Whether you’re combining two designs, or if you want to start from scratch, you’ll be adding some extra sparkle to your wedding stack in no time. Find out more about our bespoke wedding ring services <a href=\"/collections/all\" title=\"Services\">here.</a></p>",
